###### Variables
### Base URL
@BASE_URL = http://localhost:20104
### PG 거래 고유번호
@pgTxId = mockpay_tx_abc123
### 주문번호
@orderId = ORDER-001
### 결제 금액
@amount = 50000
#################################################

### Mock pay success callback
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/payments/mock-pay/success?pgTxId={{pgTxId}}&orderId={{orderId}}&amount={{amount}}

### Mock pay fail callback
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/payments/mock-pay/fail?orderId={{orderId}}&failureCode=PAY_DECLINED&failureMessage=잔액이 부족합니다
